  Source:
    Title: Mânava-dharma-sâstra
    Locus: XII 95
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Heterodoxy And Deviation
---
Whatever traditions (Smrtis) lie outside the Veda, and whatever
(works) are ill-revealed (heterodox), are all without fruit after
death, since they are said to rest in darkness.
